[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1809","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1809.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1246","title":"Microsoft Site Server 3.0 Direct Mailer 明文密码存储漏洞","description":"Microsoft Site Server 3.0 的 Direct Mailer 功能将用户域名和密码以明文形式保存在 TMLBQueue 网络共享中，该共享目录默认权限设置不当，允许网络中的任意用户访问。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过网络共享读取存储的凭据信息，进而获取系统权限。该漏洞影响 Microsoft Site Server 3.0 版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1246"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:01.790","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft KB Q229972 安全更新以解决 Direct Mailer 明文存储密码问题。如无法安装更新，手动收紧 TMLBQueue 网络共享的 NTFS 权限，仅允许授权管理员账户访问，移除 Everyone/Anonymous 写入权限，并启用 SMB 签名防止中间人窃取。建议尽快迁移至受支持的邮件服务产品，Site Server 3.0 已停止技术支持，无法获得后续安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/Q229/9/72.asp","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2068","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1246.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1246","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1246.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1246.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-99cm-v3cq-wf9j/GHSA-99cm-v3cq-wf9j.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1246.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87849/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--bcb834d4-2dd0-4c27-9456-4d8219890aab.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1809.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1800","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1800.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1233","title":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 域名解析访问限制漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 存在访问限制绕过漏洞。当用户发起初始会话请求且其 IP 地址无法反向解析为 DNS 域名时，IIS 未能正确限制该请求的访问权限，即所谓的\"域名解析\"漏洞。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过使用无法解析到 DNS 域名的 IP 地址发起初始会话请求，绕过访问控制策略，获取未授权访问。该漏洞影响 IIS 4.0 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1233"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:00.120","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-039 提供的 IIS 4.0 域限制热修复补丁（KB241562/KB241805），该补丁修正了 IIS 4.0 在 IP 地址无法解析为 DNS 域名时错误放行首次会话请求的问题。由于 IIS 4.0 及 Windows NT 4.0 已停止支持，建议升级至受支持的 Windows Server 版本（如 Windows Server 2019/2022）并部署最新版 IIS。临时缓解措施：在 IIS 管理器中禁用基于域名的访问限制策略，改为使用 IP 地址范围限制；同时确保反向 DNS 解析服务正常工作，避免因解析失败导致访问绕过。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/Q241/5/62.asp","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/657","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-039","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3306","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1233.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1233","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1233.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1233.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-53c2-2qjx-38qh/GHSA-53c2-2qjx-38qh.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/1xxx/cve-1999-1233.yaml","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1233.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--f8160a66-e7e6-44ab-9c71-410f00677cdc.json","https://github.com/RiskBasedPrioritization/RiskBasedPrioritizationAnalysis/blob/3d5cc1819ecb8cbc3aeb75d9a8260318544faf56/data_in/acme/acme_cves.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1800.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1709","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1709.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1127","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 命名管道 RPC 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 的命名管道 RPC 连接关闭机制存在缺陷，远程攻击者可通过发送包含畸形数据的连接请求，导致系统无法正常关闭无效的命名管道 RPC 连接，从而引发资源耗尽型拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 系统，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。微软已发布安全更新修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1127"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:46.667","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS98-017 提供的补丁程序（KB195733）。由于 Windows NT 4.0 已停止支持，建议升级至 Windows Server 2012 或更高版本。临时缓解措施：在防火墙层面阻止对 RPC 服务（TCP/UDP 135 端口）的匿名外部访问，并限制命名管道连接来源。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/Q195/7/33.asp","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/523.php","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-017","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1127.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1127","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1127.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1127.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1127.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/79c2cf4630fcc44f2632735de08432a07cfaf204/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fjjp-8g8w-55f2/GHSA-fjjp-8g8w-55f2.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86274/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_600_700.json","https://github.com/Team-Atlanta/aixcc-asc-atlantis/blob/785c446f980e12155935db586aa30c3b54adcc86/crs/src/crs-patch/smith/smith/lib/cwe/raw/CWE-772.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1709.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1708","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1708.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1094","title":"微软 Internet Explorer MK协议缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 4.01 及更早版本中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向用户发送包含特制长 URL 的链接（使用 \"mk:\" 协议）并诱使用户点击，触发缓冲区溢出，从而在用户系统上执行任意命令。该漏洞影响范围较广，攻击门槛较低，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1094"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:42.553","remediation":"安装 Microsoft KB Q176697 补丁，或将 Internet Explorer 升级至 4.01 Service Pack 1 及以上版本（如 IE 5.01 SP2）。对于现代系统，建议迁移至 Microsoft Edge 等受支持的浏览器，旧版 IE 已停止安全更新且不再接收补丁。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=88480839506155&w=2","http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q176/6/97.asp","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/917","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1094.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1094","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1094.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1094.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1094.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wcrg-6ghq-6288/GHSA-wcrg-6ghq-6288.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88085/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1094.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000992.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1708.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1706","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1706.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1087","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 无点IP地址安全区域绕过漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 4 在处理 URL 中的 32 位无点 IP 地址时存在解析逻辑缺陷，将点分十进制格式以外的纯数字 IP 地址误识别为主机名而非 IP 地址，导致浏览器错误地应用本地 Intranet 区域安全策略。远程攻击者可构造包含无点 IP 地址的恶意 URL，诱使用户访问后绕过正常的安全区隔离，从而执行未授权操作。该漏洞影响 Internet Explorer 4 及早期版本，增大了内网环境下的攻击面。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1087"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:41.647","remediation":"升级到 Internet Explorer 5.0 或更高版本，或改用现代浏览器（如 Edge/Chrome/Firefox）。IE 4 已停止支持且不再接收安全更新，应彻底停止使用。无法升级时可配置代理服务器过滤包含纯数字 IP 的 URL 请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q168/6/17.asp","http://www.microsoft.com/Windows/Ie/security/dotless.asp","http://www.osvdb.org/7828","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-016","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2209","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1087.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1087","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1087.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1087.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1087.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9rv3-rxw8-xr7c/GHSA-9rv3-rxw8-xr7c.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000990.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1087.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--99ba35f8-d4eb-4aae-be83-0d60e01586a1.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1706.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1687","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1687.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1055","title":"Microsoft Excel 97 工作表函数任意代码执行漏洞","description":"Microsoft Excel 97 在调用工作表函数前未向用户发出安全警告，攻击者可通过构造包含恶意 CALL 函数的 XLS 文件诱导用户打开，利用 CALL 函数加载并执行恶意 DLL，从而在目标系统上执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Microsoft Excel 97 及后续兼容版本，攻击者可通过社会工程方式诱导受害者打开特制文档触发，无需身份认证。目前已存在公开利用代码，危害较大。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1055"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:36.767","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS98-018 提供的补丁程序，该补丁可通过 https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-018 获取。同时在 Excel 中将宏安全级别设置为\"高\"以阻止未签名的 CALL 函数执行，并建议升级到 Office 2000 及以上版本以彻底规避该问题。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/179","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-018","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1737","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1055.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1055","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1055.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1055.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1055.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-cx75-p9pm-2q97/GHSA-cx75-p9pm-2q97.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_600_700.json","https://github.com/Team-Atlanta/aixcc-asc-atlantis/blob/785c446f980e12155935db586aa30c3b54adcc86/crs/src/crs-patch/smith/smith/lib/cwe/raw/CWE-356.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1055.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1687.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1051","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1051.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1335","title":"Red Hat Linux cmu-snmp snmpd 配置错误漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 4.0 系统中 cmu-snmp 软件包 3.3-1 之前版本的 snmpd 服务器存在配置错误漏洞。由于默认配置不当，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可利用该漏洞对目标系统上的敏感信息进行读取或写入操作，导致信息泄露或系统配置被篡改。该漏洞影响 Red Hat Linux 4.0 及使用相关 cmu-snmp 组件的系统，CVSS 评分 6.4，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1335"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:13.290","remediation":"升级 cmu-snmp 软件包至 3.3-1 或更高版本，并修改 SNMP 配置文件 /etc/snmp/snmpd.conf，将默认 public/private 团体字改为复杂随机字符串；同时在 iptables 防火墙中限制仅信任 IP 可访问 UDP 161 端口，禁用 SNMP 写权限（read-only）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/rh40-errata-general.html#cmu-snmp","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/7251","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e927b0fe51353a8ed03f0466aad3c47ffd172da3/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1335.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1335","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1335.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8c57fab4f71bd6fdcec1202e5361e2a9805c4950/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1335.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pr33-x2p7-6w2x/GHSA-pr33-x2p7-6w2x.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1335.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001032.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--54c919b9-3bdc-4906-ba93-56a73c55a239.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1051.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1050","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1050.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1334","title":"Elm 2.4 filter 缓冲区溢出代码执行漏洞","description":"Elm 2.4 邮件客户端的 filter 命令存在多处缓冲区溢出漏洞。攻击者可通过向受害者发送包含超长 From: 或 Reply-To: 头的恶意邮件，或诱使用户以超长 -f 参数运行 filter 命令，触发缓冲区溢出，从而在目标系统上执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Elm 2.4 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1334"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:13.147","remediation":"升级 Elm 到 2.4.5 或更高版本，该版本修复了 filter 命令中的缓冲区溢出问题。Red Hat 在 RH50 errata 中发布了针对 elm 的安全更新。如无法升级，建议禁用 filter 命令或避免使用 Elm 处理不可信来源的邮件，同时可考虑迁移至现代邮件客户端如 Thunderbird 或 Mutt。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=88609666024181&w=2","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/rh50-errata-general.html#elm","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-1334.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e927b0fe51353a8ed03f0466aad3c47ffd172da3/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1334.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1334","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8c57fab4f71bd6fdcec1202e5361e2a9805c4950/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1334.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1334.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9pwm-wh34-fpxm/GHSA-9pwm-wh34-fpxm.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1334.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001031.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1334.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1050.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1047","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1047.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1331","title":"Red Hat Linux netcfg 本地拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 4.2 中的 netcfg 2.16-1 网络配置工具存在安全配置缺陷，当特定选项被设置后，系统重启时以太网接口的控制权会被不当授予普通用户。本地攻击者可利用此漏洞在未授权的情况下关闭网络接口，导致目标系统失去网络连接能力，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Red Hat Linux 4.2 系统，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低，攻击前提是攻击者拥有本地访问权限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1331"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:12.733","remediation":"升级 netcfg 至修复版本，或应用 Red Hat RH42 errata 中针对 netcfg 的安全更新。该漏洞在 Red Hat Linux 4.2 的 netcfg 2.16-1 中存在，建议禁用 netcfg 的自动接口控制选项作为临时缓解。对于已停止支持的旧版本，建议迁移至现代受支持的 RHEL 发行版（如 RHEL 7/8/9），并确保网络管理组件保持最新安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7245.php","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/rh42-errata-general.html#netcfg","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e927b0fe51353a8ed03f0466aad3c47ffd172da3/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1331.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1331","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1331.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8c57fab4f71bd6fdcec1202e5361e2a9805c4950/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1331.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qcqp-mmmc-3pj9/GHSA-qcqp-mmmc-3pj9.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x85000/84435/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1331.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/ad7c142ce47bdca962dc5352eae3764ce44639d2/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1047.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1045","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1045.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1329","title":"Red Hat Linux SysVInit 缓冲区溢出权限提升漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 5.1 及更早版本中的 SysVInit 组件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可利用该漏洞通过向 SysVInit 发送特制的输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Red Hat Linux 5.1 及之前版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。由于攻击者需要本地访问权限，攻击门槛较高，但一旦利用成功可完全控制系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1329"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:12.473","remediation":"升级至 Red Hat Linux 5.2 或更高版本，该版本已修复 SysVInit 缓冲区溢出问题。对于已停止支持的旧版本，建议迁移至现代受支持的 RHEL 发行版（如 RHEL 7/8/9），并确保系统初始化组件保持最新安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7250.php","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/rh50-errata-general.html#SysVinit","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1329.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1329","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1329.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1329.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vcmw-4q9q-gx59/GHSA-vcmw-4q9q-gx59.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83032/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1329.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/ad7c142ce47bdca962dc5352eae3764ce44639d2/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1045.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1042","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1042.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1327","title":"Red Hat Linux linuxconf 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Linuxconf 1.11r11-rh2 版本中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，该漏洞存在于 Red Hat Linux 5.1 系统中。本地攻击者可通过向 LANG 环境变量提交超长字符串触发缓冲区溢出，成功利用此漏洞可获取系统的 root 权限。该漏洞影响范围有限，但危害严重，攻击者需要拥有本地访问权限才能利用。建议升级到不受影响的版本以修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1327"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:12.240","remediation":"升级 linuxconf 至 1.11r12 及以上版本，或升级 Red Hat Linux 至 6.0 以上版本。如无法升级，可限制本地用户设置 LANG 环境变量的权限，或移除 linuxconf 的 SUID 位作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90221103125826&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7239.php","http://www.osvdb.org/6065","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/rh51-errata-general.html#linuxconf","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1327.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1327","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1327.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1327.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-m7q8-jmgx-5r5x/GHSA-m7q8-jmgx-5r5x.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4